a cd that now lives in my car stereo how to decribe this gem of a cd . there is such a gentle warm feeling to the songs . it appears that steve kilbey 's voice is aging like a fine wine . great selection of songs with a sprinkling of five new ones . i have always tried to get friends and coworkers to like the church and this one is getting the warmest response . any fan of the church will enjoy and it is a great place to start for the curious